{"title":"凤尾鸡和秃小鸭","authors":["高瑞明"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":5,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡和秃小鸭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔幼儿故事朗诵诗〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高瑞明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡来到河边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她翘了翘尾巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理了理花冠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又伸出长靴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在水里涮了涮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她照见了自己身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地飘浮在水面："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么闪光的羽毛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么鲜艳的花冠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她高兴得转圈圈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清润一下嗓音高声唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咕咕咯，咕咕咯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的花冠多鲜艳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咕咕咯，咕咕咯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的羽毛金光闪！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嘎嘎嘎，嘎嘎嘎，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划来一只白色的小船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噢，原来是秃尾巴小鸭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在水里玩得好喜欢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她还用翅膀扑打水面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多快活："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿伸头到水里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿又飘游在水面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠悠荡荡象白色的小船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡骄傲的歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秃小鸭好象没听见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没听见吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡的歌声更傲慢："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咕咕咯，咕咕咯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的花冠多鲜艳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咕咕咯，咕咕咯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的羽毛金光闪！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秃小鸭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是那样悠闲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象小船那样靠在岸边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她抖了抖身上的水珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把翅膀扇了扇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她什么也没有听见！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊呀呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡涨红了脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛瞪得圆又圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没想到秃小鸭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连看也不看一眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的态度太傲慢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气坏了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡的歌声带着喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咕咕咯，咕咕咯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的花冠多鲜艳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咕咕咯，咕咕咯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的羽毛金光闪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“秃小鸭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上属你最难看！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咕咕咯，咕咕咯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为什么不听我唱歌？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咕咕咯，咕咕咯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为什么不朝我看一看？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊呀呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秃小鸭摇了摇秃尾巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故意地闭上双眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡伸长脖子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"憋足力气使劲喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咕咕咯，咕咕咯……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呱呱呱，呱呱呱，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传来了乌鸦的声音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把凤尾鸡的喊声打断。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是乌鸦公公飞来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他正在天空值勤旋转！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“长尾姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为什么这样叫喊？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咿？叫我‘长尾’真讨厌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我叫凤尾姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长长的尾巴象凤凰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光灿灿颜色鲜！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请问凤尾姑娘，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌鸦公公关心地："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你为什么叫喊？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚才发生了什么事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是遇见了什么危险？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“没，没，没，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是秃小鸭不肯看我一眼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧她秃秃的尾巴多难看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她不往自己窝里钻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还偏偏飘在水面上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划来划去象小船！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“乌鸦公公，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请您看一看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咕咕咯，咕咕咯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的花冠多鲜艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咕咕咯，咕咕咯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的羽毛金光闪！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咿？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌鸦公公不说话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把秃小鸭仔细看了看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秃小鸭把秃尾巴摇了摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"短短的翅膀又扇了扇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看来她不想和凤尾鸡争辩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么办？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骄傲的凤尾鸡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇上了憨厚的秃小鸭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"值勤的乌鸦公公为了难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他皱起眉头想呀想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决定自己给她们当裁判！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你们看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边飞来一只小蛾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能把它一口吞咽？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“当然是我！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡往高一蹿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一口将飞蛾吞咽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你们看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边地上爬来一只小虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能把它剁成两段？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秃小鸭刚刚走过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡扑向前："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“当然是我的嘴最尖！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呱呱呱，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌鸦公公笑了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“最鲜美的小鱼小虾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是最丰盛的午餐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能到河里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去把它们捞捡？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向河边伸脚探了探，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“扑通”一声滑进河里边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓得她乱扑乱喊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秃小鸭游过来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将凤尾鸡托举上河岸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又见她，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身划到河中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象白色小船飘在河面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把鱼虾叼在嘴边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划过来了，划过来了……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她把鱼虾一次一次送上河边！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嘎嘎嘎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我准备了丰盛的午餐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌鸦公公，凤尾姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你们入宴！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤尾鸡抖抖湿漉漉羽毛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低下头来，藏起那羞愧的脸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今天么，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌鸦公公高兴地笑了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“谁都有长也有短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用不着我来当裁判。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边有事等着我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你们自己用午餐”……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}